         <div class="giftbalance hidden_phone"><a target="_blank" href="//halifax.storecardsonline.com" style="padding: 15px 35px;" class="animated_btn hscbutton">Purchase Online</a></div>
        <p>A Halifax Shopping Centre Gift Card offers an endless number of choices! Available in any denomination from $10 and up, our fee-free gift cards always fit your budget and their style. 
Halifax Shopping Centre Gift Cards can be purchased at Guest Services or online.
<br>
<br>
<strong>We are currently improving our online gift card system. Please check back soon for a new and improved version. We apologize for any inconvenience.</strong>
</p>
        <br>
        <div class="giftbalance show_phone"><a target="_blank" href="//halifax.storecardsonline.com" style="padding: 15px 35px;" class="animated_btn hscbutton">Purchase Online</a>
            <br />
            <br />
        </div>
        <p><b>Corporate Orders</b><br/> Our Gift Cards make a great incentive or gift for employees and colleagues. If you are interested in placing a corporate order, please contact Allyson Boyd, Guest Services Supervisor, at (902) 454-8666 or at <a href="mailto:Allyson.Boyd@cushwake.com">Allyson.Boyd@cushwake.com</a>. Halifax Shopping Centre provides incentives for larger corporate gift card orders. Contact us to learn more!</p>
        
